==Maintaining the window==

Set up a window procedure to be run each time <code>WE_PAINT</code> is called.

:;<nowiki>Example:</nowiki>

<pre>
static void MyWindowProc(Window *w, WindowEvent *e)
{
	switch (e->event) {
		case WE_PAINT: {
			DrawWindowWidgets(w);
		}	break;
	}
}
</pre>

